    "description": "Whispers of Gold is a choice-driven visual novel set in a medieval free city. You are Arthur, a mercenary trying to make ends meet who investigates the abduction of a scion. On your journey, you will have to make a lot of difficult decisions. To kill or to spare? To get to the bottom of the mystery or to give in to greed?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 hours of gameplay;<br></li><li>8 main endings, one secret ending, and many ways to die at someone’s hand;<br></li><li>Mini-games;<br></li><li>A medieval setting with its own unique inner-workings;<br></li><li>Authentic visual presentation;<br></li><li>Original soundtrack.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game mechanics: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Looking for clues will be your top aide in solving mysteries and learning the truth. What can a room reveal about its owner?</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256750/extras/d13a340dec49e2c32ae154e90a375c48.poster.avif?t=1712657752\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256750/extras/d13a340dec49e2c32ae154e90a375c48.webm?t=1712657752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256750/extras/d13a340dec49e2c32ae154e90a375c48.mp4?t=1712657752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick locks to get to the hard-to-reach answers. What secrets are being hidden away from prying eyes?</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256750/extras/1c2d11125f242bfcb769c8628436a288.poster.avif?t=1712657752\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256750/e